{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487381275,"sessionID":"ses_0bfe020b5ffeoZNo5CdAcudSTe","part":{"id":"prt_f4021be96001g7QVBXOhK3IB7i","messageID":"msg_f4021aff1001X8Dp7Wh4MLG3fB","sessionID":"ses_0bfe020b5ffeoZNo5CdAcudSTe","type":"text","text":"The YAML supports the exact override: when `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` is present, it binds `artifact_dir` directly and skips the resolver command. I’m checking whether the existing fan-out runner can execute this single detached lineage without violating the “only write this lineage directory” boundary.","time":{"start":1783487381142,"end":1783487381274},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_04d4e2175377943b016a4ddb9525e481919c3be571725316c6","phase":"commentary"}}}}
