ation 4 of the deep-review wave and append the canonical JSONL record.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"deep_loop_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"deep-review continuation with append semantics\"}\n49: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-049\",\"bucket\":\"deep_loop_prompts\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-edge\",\"prompt\":\"Use the deep-research workflow, not a manual loop, to investigate routing drift.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"deep_loop_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"workflow selection still implies write-producing run\"}\n50: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-050\",\"bucket\":\"deep_loop_prompts\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Launch a convergence-tracked deep review on the docs packet.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"deep_loop_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"review-loop initiation\"}\n51: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-051\",\"bucket\":\"skill_routing_prompts\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Find code that does graph-query blending when Grep is not enough.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"no\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"skill_routing_only\",\"skill_top_1\":\"system-code-graph\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"code search request\"}\n52: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-053\",\"bucket\":\"skill_routing_prompts\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Use Chrome DevTools to capture a HAR for the reducer dashboard failing in staging.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"no\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"skill_routing_only\",\"skill_top_1\":\"mcp-chrome-devtools\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"browser-debugging connector task\"}\n\n(Showing lines 18-52 of 193. Use offset=53 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"id\":\"rr-iter2-018\",\"bucket\":\"true_read_only\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Explain t